title: 8. What Made People Like Kobe Bryant, Jesus Christ, or Adolf Hitler Some of the Most Influential People In History?
itunes:title: 8. What Made People Like Kobe Bryant, Jesus Christ, or Adolf Hitler Some of the Most Influential People In History?
description: What does it take to build a real legacy? Jesus Christ, Adolf Hitler, Kobe Bryant… no matter what their goal was, it was very clear that each one was highly skilled in influencing people, culture, and the world.
